        <mxCell id="t_changes_list" parent="1" style="text;html=1;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top" value="Already on dev (ships on next dev→master deploy):&lt;br&gt;  ✓ Grafana pinned to manager (constraints: node.role==manager)&lt;br&gt;  ✓ App dashboard fixed — up{job=&quot;itu-minitwit-app&quot;} + Uptime% panel&lt;br&gt;  ✓ Logging dashboard fixed — {swarm_service=&quot;minitwit_webserver&quot;}&lt;br&gt;  ✓ UFW firewall rules on all 3 nodes&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Triggered by the deploy itself:&lt;br&gt;  • Webserver .2 on Worker-1 gets re-scheduled against new digest → Rejected state clears&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Still to do before simulator URL flips to DO:&lt;br&gt;  1. Back `latest` counter with Postgres (sim_api.go:13 is still in-process — flaky under 3 replicas)&lt;br&gt;  2. Merge course PR (repositories.py → devtroopersminitwit.codes)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Post-flip cleanup:&lt;br&gt;  3. Decommission Hetzner after 48h of clean DO-only traffic&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Backlog:&lt;br&gt;  4. Rotate the plaintext ghcr.io PAT (currently in Swarm secrets)&lt;br&gt;  5. tecnativa/docker-socket-proxy in front of Traefik + Promtail" vertex="1">
